George Ernest https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Ernest 0 George Ernest (November 20, 1921 – June 25, 2009) was an American actor and Office of Strategic Services (OSS) combat photographer/cameraman during World War II. He appeared in more than 60 films between 1930 and 1942.
